review 1: Breakfast was great and location is exceptional, would stay there again.  The hotel is excellent, the bedrooms are spectacular.
review 2: I love the beauty of the land. I feel welcome and comfortable. One of my favorite place after home. The food taste so yummy. The view from the terrace was great. The view from the restaurat was beautiful. I love it. Will return one day.
review 3: I was here and I love it. The view is beautiful. The surrounding is very relaxing. I like the people here too. The are very friendly. Recommended place to escape from daily routine. Will come back.
review 4: Beautiful, relaxing place in the middle of the forest, away from the tourist trail. Friendly people, delicious on prem harvested fruit and vegetables. Recommended for a quite break. from everyday life
review 5: Marvelous place for relax. View is fantastic. Fresh harvest fruits from the garden was so nice. The taste of the fresh veggies was so sweet. I love it and will come back.
